 Accela Automation
 File: CapConditionScript.java
 
 Accela, Inc.
 Copyright (C): 2002-2014
 
 Description:
 Provides the "aa.capCondition" object through which script writers can
 operate on an retrieve CapCondition related objects.
 
 Notes:
